# Core Application Logic

The primary application code resides in the `app/` directory.

- **Layout:** The main application layout is defined in [app/layout.tsx](mdc:app/layout.tsx).
- **Homepage:** The entry point and homepage content is in [app/page.tsx](mdc:app/page.tsx).
- **Global Styles:** Global CSS styles are applied via [app/globals.css](mdc:app/globals.css).
